0Lucas%20Webber%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Soufan%20Center%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20think%20tank%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20would%20have%20required%20%26quot%3Bquite%20a%20bit%20of%20planning%20and%20preparation%20beforehand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20also%20illustrated%20%26quot%3Bthe%20diverse%20range%20of%20militant%20actors%20Russia%20has%20angered%20through%20its%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20policy%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20reported%20that%20the%20Islamic%20State's%20(IS)%20Northern%20Caucasus%20branch%2C%20Wilayat%20Kavkaz%2C%20was%20likely%20behind%20the%20attacks%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20had%20%26quot%3Bincreased%20fears%20within%20the%20Russian%20information%20space%20about%20further%20terrorist%20attacks%20and%20instability%20in%20the%20North%20Caucasus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20of%20the%20six%20gunmen%20said%20to%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20attack%20also%20had%20connections%20to%20the%20Dagestan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdagestan-anti-jewish-airport-rampage-was-egged-on-by-telegram-channel-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregion's%3C%2Fa%3E%20political%20elite%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcepa.org%2Farticle%2Fislamists-feast-as-russias-security-state-slumbers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Washington%20DC-based%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20destruction%20after%20more%20than%2015%20police%20officers%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20armed%20attacks%20in%20Makhachkala%20checkpoint%20and%20a%20synagogue%20in%20Derbent%2C%20in%20Dagestan%2C%20Russia%20on%20June%2024%2C%202024.%20Describing%20it%20as%20a%20'terrorist%20attack%2C'%20the%20Republic's%20head%2C%20Sergey%20Melikov%20said%3A%20'We%20know%20who%20is%20behind%20this%20and%20what%20the%20organizers%20of%20these%20attacks%20aimed%20for.%20War%20has%20come%20to%20our%20home.'%20Active%20phase%20of%20counter-terrorism%20operations%20in%20Makhachkala%20and%20Derbent%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20and%20six%20gunmen%20responsible%20for%20the%20attacks%20were%20neutralized.%20(Photo%20by%20National%20Antiterrorism%20Committee%20%2F%20Handout%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667e9451d1c84a0eaca89906%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAround%2020%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20armed%20attacks%20in%20Makhachkala%20and%20Derbent.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20marked%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20major%20domestic%20security%20failures%20that%20have%20plagued%20Russia%20since%20it%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20incidents%20have%20presented%20a%20major%20problem%20for%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20whose%20reputation%20as%20a%20strongman%20able%20to%20guarantee%20security%20and%20order%20in%20Russia%20while%20also%20waging%20a%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20appears%20to%20be%20flailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20security%20forces%20stormed%20a%20detention%20center%20in%20the%20southern%20Russian%20city%20of%20Rostov-on-Don%20where%20six%20inmates%20linked%20to%20Islamic%20State%20had%20taken%20two%20guards%20hostage.%20The%20inmates%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20the%20hostages%20were%20freed%2C%20Russian%20news%20agency%20Tass%20reported%2C%20citing%20Russia's%20Federal%20Penitentiary%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20gunmen%20entered%20the%20packed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisis-k-allowed-slipped-into-moscow-massacre-because-war-zelenskyy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrocus%20City%20Hall%20concert%20venue%20in%20Moscow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20killing%20more%20than%20140%20people%20and%20leaving%20many%20more%20injured.%20Four%20men%20from%20Tajikistan%20were%20detained%20following%20the%20attack.%20Islamic%20State%20later%20claimed%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20a%20mob%20of%20protesters%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdagestan-anti-jewish-airport-rampage-was-egged-on-by-telegram-channel-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eransacked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Dagestan's%20main%20airport%20in%20search%20of%20Jewish%20people%20to%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b13bd34-e537-4e93-9d19-9e7030543b75%5C%22%3ENorth%20Caucasus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20North%20Caucasus%20region%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20rebellion%20against%20Kremlin%20rule%2C%20especially%20in%20Chechnya%2C%20where%20Russia%20battled%20separatists%20in%20two%20bloody%20wars%20%E2%80%94%20in%201994-1996%20and%20then%20in%201999-2009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20violence%20became%20increasingly%20rare%2C%20with%20immense%20pressure%20from%20security%20services%20and%20developments%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%20causing%20Islamic%20State's%20presence%20in%20the%20Caucasus%20to%20splinter%2C%20Mark%20Youngman%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthreatologist.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThreatologist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20analyzes%20Eurasian%20security%20risks%20and%20specializes%20in%20the%20North%20Caucasus%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%202017%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20organized%20insurgency%20%E2%80%94%20no%20infrastructure%2C%20no%20leadership%20%E2%80%94%20challenging%20Russia's%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20Youngman%20said.%20%26quot%3BSince%20that%20point%2C%20most%20jihadist%20violence%20has%20been%20perpetrated%20by%20isolated%20individuals%20and%2