%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%2C%20moderate%20rain%20is%20defined%20as%20rainfall%20amounting%20to%20between%207.6%20and%2035.5%20mm%20in%20a%20day%2C%20and%20heavy%20rain%20is%20rainfall%20amounting%20to%20between%2064.5%20and%20124.4%20mm%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20recorded%20a%20minimum%20temperature%20of%2028%20degrees%20Celsius%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20maximum%20temperature%20is%20likely%20to%20settle%20around%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20the%20IMD%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20humidity%20levels%20stood%20at%2080%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20was%20recorded%20in%20the%20'moderate'%20category%20with%20a%20reading%20of%20108%20at%209%20am%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%20zero%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20'good'%2C%2051%20and%20100%20'satisfactory'%2C%20101%20and%20200%20'moderate'%2C%20201%20and%20300%20'poor'%2C%20301%20and%20400%20'very%20poor'%2C%20and%20401%20and%20500%20'severe'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20raining%20devastation%20on%20a%20city%20ill-prepared%20for%20a%20three-hour%20downpour%20that%20led%20to%20the%20roof%20of%20Delhi%20airport's%20Terminal-1%20collapsing%2C%20killing%20one%20person%20and%20suspending%20flight%20operations%2C%20and%20inundated%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20others%20were%20killed%20in%20rain-related%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20recorded%20228.1%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20highest%20since%201936%20for%20the%20month%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%2C%20228.1%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20was%20recorded%20at%20Safdarjung%2C%20the%20city's%20primary%20weather%20station%2C%20192.8%20mm%20at%20Lodhi%20Road%2C%20Mausam%20Bhavan%2C%20150.4%20mm%20at%20Ridge%2C%20106.6%20mm%20at%20Palam%2C%20and%2066.3%20mm%20at%20Ayanagar.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0