he%20conclusion%20of%20this%20week's%20presidential%20debate%20between%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20many%20that%20the%2081-year-old%20Biden%20may%20not%20be%20capable%20of%20winning%20the%20general%20election%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20inability%20to%20clearly%20communicate%20during%20the%2090-minute%20debate%20earned%20harsh%20criticism%20from%20across%20the%20US%20political%20spectrum%2C%20most%20notably%20among%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVan%20Jones%2C%20a%20former%20official%20in%20the%20Obama%20administration%20and%20CNN%20analyst%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsg.news.yahoo.com%2Fex-obama-adviser-van-jones-045230154.html%3Fguccounter%3D1%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Biden%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20a%20test%20to%20meet%20tonight%20to%20restore%20confidence%20in%20the%20country%20and%20of%20the%20base%2C%20and%20he%20failed%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20far%20from%20our%20convention.%20And%20there%20is%20time%20for%20this%20party%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20different%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20did%20land%20a%20few%20blows%20on%20his%20predecessor%20over%20Trump's%20various%20personal%20indiscretions%20and%20the%20January%206%202021%20insurrection%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol%2C%20saying%20at%20one%20point%2C%20%E2%80%9Cyou've%20got%20the%20morals%20of%20an%20alley%20cat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20persuade%20many%20sceptics%20that%20Biden%20is%20capable%20of%20fighting%20off%20the%20Trump%20campaign%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20performing%20the%20duties%20of%20US%20commander-in-chief%20and%20the%20hardest%20job%20in%20the%20world%20for%20another%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20polls%20over%20the%20weekend%20show%20Biden%20is%20losing%20support%20after%20his%20dreadful%20debate%20performance%2C%20which%20seems%20highly%20likely%2C%20the%20move%20to%20replace%20him%20as%20the%20Democrats'%20candidate%20will%20become%20even%20more%20intense%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20irresistible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20would%20this%20play%20out%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPersuading%20Biden%20to%20step%20aside%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20withering%20criticism%20from%20his%20party%2C%20Biden%20remains%20in%20control%20of%20his%20fate.%20He%20won%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalreview.com%2Fcorner%2Freminder-biden-has-3894-or-99-of-pledged-dnc-delegates%2F%5C%22%3E99%25%20of%20the%20pledged%20delegates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Democratic%20primary%20process%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20meaning%20he%20is%20entitled%20to%20the%20nomination.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20any%20decision%20to%20move%20to%20a%20different%20candidate%20starts%20with%20Biden%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsent%20dramatic%20health%20news%20or%20his%20removal%20under%20the%2025th%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fhouse%2F4746165-speaker-johnson-cabinet-biden-25th-amendment%2F%5C%22%3Eallows%20for%20such%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20vice%20president%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20cabinet%20if%20the%20president%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunable%20to%20discharge%20the%20powers%20and%20duties%20of%20his%20office%E2%80%9D%2C%20Biden%20would%20have%20to%20agree%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20party's%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20should%20be%20realistic%20here%3A%20Biden%20is%20a%20very%20stubborn%20man.%20You%20don't%20get%20to%20be%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20without%20being%20enormously%20self-confident.%20Biden%20may%20not%20be%20the%20smartest%20or%20most%20talented%20politician%2C%20but%20he%20is%20dogged%20and%20relentless%20in%20his%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20ran%20for%20president%20twice%20before%20his%20success%20in%202020.%20He%20didn't%20let%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.co