til%20Versha%20had%20to%20rush%20out%20due%20to%20a%20family%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20man%20finished%20the%20food%20and%20called%20for%20the%20check%2C%20the%20bill%20stunned%20him%20-%20he%20owed%20the%20cafe%20an%20obscene%20Rs%201%2C21%2C917.70%20for%20food%20that%20should%20not%20cost%20more%20than%20a%20few%20thousand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20promptly%20disputed%20the%20bill%20but%20he%20was%20threatened%2C%20confined%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20pay.%20The%20man%20ended%20up%20transferring%20the%20amount%20online%20to%20one%20of%20the%20cafe's%20owners%20-%2032-year-old%20Akshay%20Pahwa.%20Mr%20Pahwa%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Shahdara%20in%20East%20Delhi%20and%20has%20studied%20till%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20out%20of%20the%20cafe%2C%20he%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20cops%20and%20filed%20a%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20set%20out%20to%20probe%20the%20case%20and%20a%20four-member%20team%20led%20by%20Inspector%20Sanjay%20Gupta%20was%20formed.%20Soon%2C%20Mr%20Pahwa%20was%20in%20the%20police's%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20he%20told%20the%20police%20that%20the%20Black%20Mirror%20cafe%20is%20owned%20by%20him%2C%20Ansh%20Grover%2C%20and%20Vansh%20Pahwa.%20Akshay%20and%20Vansh%20are%20cousins%2C%20while%20Ansh%20is%20their%20friend.%20The%20cafe%20employs%20several%20%26quot%3Btable%20managers%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20one%20man%20named%20Aryan%3B%20and%20these%20%26quot%3Btable%20managers%26quot%3B%20are%20managed%20by%20one%20Digranshu%2C%20he%20said.%20Aryan%20is%20a%20Class%207%20dropout%20and%20is%20currently%20unemployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pahwa%20also%20gave%20up%20Versha%20-%2025-year-old%20Afsan%20Parveen%2C%20who%20also%20goes%20by%20the%20names%20Ayesha%20and%20Noor.%20When%20the%20cops%20tracked%20her%20down%2C%20Ms%20Parveen%20was%20at%20another%20cafe%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bdate%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20man%20from%20Mumbai%20she%20had%20met%20on%20Shaadi.com.%