aten%20tag.%20Now%2C%20the%20side%20will%20be%20having%20another%20chance%20to%20end%20its%20long%20wait%20of%20ICC%20title%20drought%20when%20it%20faces%20the%20Proteas%20in%20the%20final%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20hilariously%20said%20that%20Rohit%20might%20jump%20in%20the%20Barbados%20ocean%20if%20India%20lose%20the%20upcoming%20final%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20played%20two%20World%20Cup%20finals%20where%20he%20has%20gone%20into%20the%20final%20unbeaten.%20That%20speaks%20of%20his%20captaincy%20and%20leadership%20quality%20and%20I'm%20not%20surprised%20because%20he%20became%20captain%20when%20I%20was%20the%20BCCI%20president%20and%20when%20Virat%20didn't%20want%20to%20captain%20India%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ganguly%20as%20quoted%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20make%20him%20captain%20because%20he%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20captain.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20pushing%20from%20all%20of%20us%20to%20make%20him%20captain%20and%20I'm%20very%20happy%20to%20see%20the%20progress%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20under%20him.%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20said%20winning%20IPL%20titles%20could%20sometimes%20be%20more%20challenging%20because%20of%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20has%20the%20record%20of%20winning%20five%20IPL%20titles%2C%20which%20is%20a%20huge%20achievement.%20Winning%20an%20IPL%20sometimes%20is%20more%20difficult.%20Don't%20misquote%20me%2C%20I'm%20not%20saying%20IPL%20is%20better%20than%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20you%20have%20to%20win%2016-17%20(12-13)%20matches%20to%20win%20an%20IPL%3B%20here%20you%20need%20to%20win%208-9%20matches%20to%20win%20a%20World%20Cup.%20The%20honour%