0Donald%20Trump's%20October%2C%202023%20testimony%20in%20his%20New%20York%20civil%20fraud%20trial%2C%20in%20which%20says%20that%20he%20is%20the%20sole%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20trust%20that%20owns%20everything%20under%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20umbrella.%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20apparent%20failings%20in%20the%20moral-turpitude%20department%20also%20put%20him%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFelony%20convictions%20are%20universally%20considered%20crimes%20of%20moral%20turpitude%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peter%20M.%20Rhodes%2C%20partner%20at%20the%20Haddonfield%2C%20New%20Jersey-based%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcahill-law.com%2Fteam%2Fpeter-m-rhodes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECahill%2C%20Wilinski%2C%20Rhodes%20%26amp%3B%20Joyce.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20his%20felony%20conviction%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20license%20is%20owned%20by%20a%20trust%20whose%20sole%20beneficiary%20is%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20then%20that%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20violates%20the%20ABC%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rhodes%2C%20whose%20firm%20has%20served%20for%2050%20years%20as%20counsel%20to%20the%20New%20Jersey%20Licensed%20Beverage%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20three%20New%20Jersey%20licenses%20are%20owned%20by%20LLCs%2C%20and%20Trump's%20namesake%20son%20is%20the%20president%20and%20license%20signatory%20for%20each%20one%2C%20according%20to%20records%20reviewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221518%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%2C%20Jr.'s%20signature%20on%20the%20most%20recent%20liquor%20license%20for%20his%20father's%20golf%20course%20in%20Bedminster%2C%20NJ.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667f096240cf2af6e4f6db65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20Jr.'s%20signature%20on%20the%20most%20recent%20liquor%20license%20for%20his%20fa