mentary%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDancers%20are%20always%20being%20taken%20advantage%20of.%20We're%20paid%20late%2C%20certain%20jobs%20don't%20have%20the%20best%20working%20conditions%20or%20the%20best%20rates.%20Companies%20wanting%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20genuinely%20talented%20people%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20not%20something%20new.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20different%20version%20that%20nobody%20has%20seen%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatching%20as%20this%20organization%20in%20an%20organized%20manner%20take%20advantage%20of%20dancers%2C%20doing%20what%20it%20did%20to%20their%20families%20%E2%80%94%20I%20couldn't%20let%20that%20be.%20I've%20been%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20almost%2014%20years%20now.%20I've%20pursued%20dance%20professionally%2C%20I%20opened%20my%20own%20dance%20studio.%20I've%20been%20filming%20dancers%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20time%20I've%20been%20here%2C%20and%20I've%20created%20an%20immense%20amount%20of%20content.%20I've%20seen%20these%20situations%2C%20heard%20all%20these%20stories%2C%20and%20been%20in%20situations%20where%20things%20felt%20unfair.%20When%20I%20saw%20that%20video%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20wasn't%20just%20trying%20to%20help%20their%20family.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20help%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Melanie%20Wilking%20in%20%26quot%3BDancing%20for%20the%20Devil%3A%20The%207M%20TikTok%20Cult.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66671760ed9a404d829c1a38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMelanie%20Wilking%20in%20%26quot%3BDancing%20for%20the%20Devil%3A%20The%207M%20TikTok%20Cult.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20approach%20the%20Wilking%20family%20and%20Melanie%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20participate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20long%20process%20of%20maintaining%20a%20relationship%20with%20them.%20At%20first%20it%20was%20just%20me%2C%20then%20it%20was%20Jessica%20%5BAcevedo%2C%20an%20executive%20producer%5D.%20It%20was%20building%20a%20foundation%20of%20trust%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20handle%20this%20with%20the%20utmost%20care%2C%20that%20we%20weren't%20out%20to%20just%20make%20some%20money%20or%20make%20a%20thing%20about%20their%20family%20to%20try%20to%20exploit%20them.%20Because%20that%20was%20absolutely%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20five%20months%20were%20brutal.%20We%20reached%20out%20to%20friends%20of%207M%20members%2C%20as%20well%20as%20choreographers%20who%20worked%20with%20them.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20scared%3B%20they%20were%20hesitant%20to%20comment%20or%20be%20involved.%20Nobody%20wanted%20to%20take%20the%20risk.%20And%20we%20didn't%20really%20know%20the%20details%20of%20what%20was%20happening.%20We%20were%20digging%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20just%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%2C%20what%20really%20is%20this%20thing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20needed%20%5Bthe%20Wilkings%5D%20to%20know%20that%20all%20of%20us%2C%20including%20them%2C%20were%20in%20alignment%20on%20what%20we%20wanted%20the%20outcome%20to%20be.%20And%20because%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20situation%20that%20Miranda%20was%20in%2C%20it's%20very%20hard%20for%20any%20family%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20the%20Wilkings%20%E2%80%94%20to%20know%20what%20the%20right%20thing%20is%20to%20do%20in%20that%20situation.%20So%20yeah%2C%20it%20took%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20talked%20to%20Isaiah%20since%20he%20left%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20remained%20in%20contact%20a%20little%20bit%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202020%2C%20but%20we%20just%20stopped%20talking%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20hope%20for%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Isaiah%20is%20a%20victim%20whether%20or%20not%20he%20benefits%20from%20being%20in%20the%20business%20with%20his%20dad.%20Isaiah%20is%20somebody%20who%20I%20used%20to%20call%20a%20friend%2C%20and%20hopefully%20can%20call%20a%20friend%20again.%20I%20would%20genuinely%20love%20for%20that%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20hope%20the%20series'%20impact%20will%20be%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20this%20organization%20to%20stop%20what%20it's%20doing.%20I%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20future%20where%20every%20victim%20of%20this%20thing%20comes%20out%20of%20it%20and%20finds%20their%20own%20path%20in%20life.%20To%20me%2C%20that's%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%20Seeing%20this%20at%20No.%201%20on%20Netflix%20was%20a%20surreal%20moment%20of%20some%20victory.%20When%20people%20say%20congratulations%2C%20there's%20a%20bit%20of%20bittersweet%20sorrow%20because%20I%20want%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20documentary%2C%20which%20might%20not%20come%20right%20away.%20And%20hopefully%20the%20impact%20is%20that%20people%20put%20pressure%20on%20this%20organization%20and%20put%20pressure%20on%20Robert.%20That's%20the%20only%20way%20that%20any%20kind%20of%20change%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20the%20moment%20of%20this%20interview%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdancing-for-the-devil-miranda-derrick-wasnt-brainwashed-robert-shinn-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiranda%20is%20still%20in%20the%20organization%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20initially%20the%20driving%20force%20for%20me%20to%20want%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20pursuing%20this.%20It%20was%20not%20to%20get%20a%20Netflix%20documentary.%20It%20was%20the%20outcome%20that%20still%20hasn't%20happened%20yet.%20So%20when%20I%20hear%20Congratulations%2C%20it's%20No.%201%2C%20that's%20awesome.%20But%20I%20can't%20fully%20accept%20it.%20I%20feel%20a%20certain%20sadness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20documentary%20filmmaker.%20My%20origin%20is%20filming%20dance%2C%20being%20a%20dancer%2C%20and%20providing%20a%20physical%20space%20for%20people%20to%20train%2