%20to%20vegetable%20farming%20on%20over%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20Smarika%20quitting%20her%20job%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20farmer%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20she%20claims%20to%20have%20received%20a%20production%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20of%20tomato%20per%20acre%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20in%20the%20previous%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20why%20you%20should%20grow%20vegetables!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%20have%20longer%20growth%20cycles%20which%20are%20generally%20twice%20a%20year.%20Vegetable%20farming%2C%20however%2C%20gives%20multiple%20harvests%20as%20the%20growth%20cycles%20are%20shorter%20and%20are%20more%20profitable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVegetable%20farming%20offers%20a%20triple%20win%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351525%2Ffarming-profitable-how-to-make-natural-pesticides-himachal-couple-zero-budget-natural-earns-double%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20income%20for%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20traders%2C%20enhanced%20consumer%20health%20and%20a%20rejuvenated%20economy.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20when%20vegetables%20rise%2C%20people%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dilip%20Rajan%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20at%20the%20East-West%20Seed%20Global%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmarika%20realised%20this%20fact%20and%20first%20worked%20on%20getting%20the%20land%20ready%20for%20vegetable%20cultivation.%20The%20first%20vegetable%20she%20grew%20was%20tomato%2C%20seeking%20help%20from%20an%20agricultural%20consultant%20to%20make%20the%20transition%20smooth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201599px)%20100vw%2C%201599px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22h