ld%20have%20a%20compelling%20tale%20to%20tell.%20In%20June%202021%2C%20actor%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20who%20was%20promoting%20his%20film%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%20Kare%20Aashiqui%E2%80%99%20first%20donated%20the%20truck%20to%20Dhananjay.%20However%2C%20what%20was%20meant%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20her%20be%20financially%20independent%20had%20the%20opposite%20effect%20when%20local%20authorities%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20run%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20denied%20a%20license%20and%20the%20truck%20had%20to%20be%20parked%20in%20a%20nearby%20school%20for%20almost%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhananjay%20says.%20But%20today%2C%20things%20have%20changed%20for%20the%20better.%20While%20she%20shares%20that%20sales%20are%20not%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20currently%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThe%20heat%20is%20too%20much%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20many%20customers%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20she%20maintains%20that%20at%20least%20she%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F256969%2Fmumbai-heroes-of-humanity-humanity-heroes-first-transgender-photojournalist-zoya-thomas-lobo-transgender-community-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20business%20to%20call%20her%20own%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20story%20is%20a%20testament%20of%20reform%20and%20promise%3B%20it%20is%20also%20a%20nod%20to%2018-year-old%20Ishnoor%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20help%20the%20trans%20community%20regain%20their%20footing%20in%20the%20quest%20for%20financial%20independence.%20His%20endeavour%20to%20help%20trans%20persons%20revive%20their%20businesses%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%E2%80%98SoulSpectrum%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20small%20but%20significant%20step%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20bringing%20a%20radical%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20businesses%20run%20by%20trans%20individuals%20are%20perceived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20s